description_html:
HUT collection by Ryusuke Fukusada is the teakwood outdoor collection where the concept is based on the EASTxWEST. Outdoor furniture has been inspired from mostly from the WEST culture...but as today..the trend of outdoor has been moving forward the EAST. Therefore, we have designed the outdoor piece that was inspired from the EAST concept and perfectly match into the scene of both culture.
material are in teakwood with walnut oil stained with stainless steel powder coated.
